{"tid":2188590,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［突發］海關去左觀塘黃店拉負責人 原來係佢派眾志”not made in China” 口罩","createTime":"2020-09-04T10:38:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-04T16:38:49.000Z","uid":22556,"like":4,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"f98cd081688612505dc964791c6c87681b250859","tid":2188590,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T10:38:16.000Z","msg":"現已解散的「香港眾志」今年 4 月宣布搜購逾 100 萬個口罩，再包裝成「自救口罩」，惟之後海關拘捕兩名眾志成員，指涉違反《商品說明條例》。眾志當時聲明引述海關指，若口罩生產於香港或台灣，可能不符合包裝盒上「Not made in China」的標示，可能違反法例。《立場新聞》收到讀者報料，指海關人員今（4 日)午突然到觀塘黃店「favilla」，指店內派發的口罩懷疑違反《商品說明條例》。<br />\n<br />\n海關回覆《立場新聞》表示，有網上商戶透過餐廳食肆供應一款附有「NOT MADE IN CHINA」及「ASTM Level 1」等標示的外科口罩，懷疑附有虛假產地及效能聲稱。海關指，由於該商戶一直未能提供認證，證明相關口罩符合所作的標示聲稱，海關於 5 月 22 日及 25 日分別拘捕該商戶涉嫌違反《商品說明條例》的一名代表及一名董事。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%B5%B7%E9%97%9C%E6%90%9C%E8%A7%80%E5%A1%98%E9%BB%83%E5%BA%97-%E7%96%91%E6%B6%89%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97-%E8%87%AA%E6%95%91%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9-%E6%9B%BE%E7%A8%B1%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9-not-made-in-china-%E6%A8%99%E7%A4%BA-%E9%81%95%E5%95%86%E5%93%81%E8%AA%AA%E6%98%8E%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B/?fbclid=IwAR3ThxkBLabjS9NNZgz_lxFcR1sjbDxE-eRa14GkPwTTLgVwMNB8yPvYJ4c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E9%2597%259C%25E6%2590%259C%25E8%25A7%2580%25E5%25A1%2598%25E9%25BB%2583%25E5%25BA%2597-%25E7%2596%2591%25E6%25B6%2589%25E7%259C%25BE%25E5%25BF%2597-%25E8%2587%25AA%25E6%2595%2591%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%25BD%25A9-%25E6%259B%25BE%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%25BD%25A9-not-made-in-china-%25E6%25A8%2599%25E7%25A4%25BA-%25E9%2581%2595%25E5%2595%2586%25E5%2593%2581%25E8%25AA%25AA%25E6%2598%258E%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3ThxkBLabjS9NNZgz_lxFcR1sjbDxE-eRa14GkPwTTLgVwMNB8yPvYJ4c&d=HMiOmB7b1AqxO%2BCwCPl1cYMY%2BwsNvTr2Nz54cwdIBJg%3D&h=66ef26c0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E9%2597%259C%25E6%2590%2